#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.dolphin-plugins.metainfo.xml:7
msgid "Dolphin Plugins"
msgstr "Plugins de Dophin"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.dolphin-plugins.metainfo.xml:8
msgid ""
"Dolphin integration for revision control systems, Dropbox, and disk images"
msgstr ""
"Integration de Dolphin per systemas de controlo de revision, Dropbox e "
"images de disco"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.dolphin-plugins.metainfo.xml:10
msgid ""
"These plugins integrate Dolphin with the revision control systems Bazaar, "
"Mercurial and Git. A Dropbox plugin gives action items to keep your files "
"synced to the Dropbox service. A disk image integration plugin adds a mount "
"or unmount action."
msgstr ""
"Iste plugins integra Dolphin con le systemsa de controlo de revision Bazaar, "
"Mercurial e Git. Un plugin de Dropbox da elementos de action pro mantener tu "
"file synchronisate al servicio de Dropbox. Un plugin de integration de image "
"de disc adde un action de montar e dismontar."
